Description: Q-Free ASA is a Norway-based company engaged in the field of Intelligent Transport System (ITS) that improve traffic flow, road safety, and air quality. The Company provides services within two areas: Road User Charging (RUC) and Advanced Transportation Management System (ATMS). The RUC solutions reduce traffic and offer traffic congestion management. The ATMS area is responsible for the improvement of traffic flow and safety by collecting, processing and communication of information about types of traffic. It offers urban traffic management central, parking management, truck tolling, Automatic License Plate Registration (ALPS), passengers, cargo and transport management, as well as traffic detection, among others. It business activities are divided into three segments: Tolling, Traffic Management and Assets held for sale. Q-Free operates worldwide.
